cu.explanation_en: Setting GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NG_AMF to invalid IP '192.168.8.256' (octet 256 > 255) will cause NG-AMF interface binding failure and connection error.

du.explanation_en: Setting physCellId to string '0' instead of number will cause type mismatch and cell identification failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 physCellId 設定為字串 '0' 而非數字會導致類型不匹配並造成小區識別失敗。
